data.name: ReadStatsReport
data.value: select YEAR_MONTH, FIRST_RUN_NUMBER, LINE_NUMBER, CREATED_TIMESTAMP, SERVICE_PRVDR_ID, OFFICE_ID, CASE_WRK_ROLE, CASE_EFF_DATE, PARENT_ID, CHIEF_ID, COLUMN1, COLUMN2, COLUMN3, COLUMN4, COLUMN5, COLUMN6, COLUMN7, COLUMN8, COLUMN9, COLUMN10, COLUMN11, COLUMN12, COLUMN13, COLUMN14, COLUMN15 from CKT_STATS_REPORT where (YEAR_MONTH = @yearMonth) and (FIRST_RUN_NUMBER = @firstRunNumber) and (LINE_NUMBER = 27) and (OFFICE_ID >= @officeId) and ( (OFFICE_ID > @officeId) or ( (OFFICE_ID = @officeId) and (SERVICE_PRVDR_ID > @servicePrvdrId) ) ) order by OFFICE_ID, SERVICE_PRVDR_ID

data.name: UpdateStatsReport
data.value: update CKT_STATS_REPORT set COLUMN1 = @column1, COLUMN2 = @column2, COLUMN3 = @column3, COLUMN4 = @column4, COLUMN5 = @column5, COLUMN6 = @column6, COLUMN7 = @column7, COLUMN8 = @column8, COLUMN9 = @column9, COLUMN10 = @column10, COLUMN11 = @column11, COLUMN12 = @column12, COLUMN13 = @column13, COLUMN14 = @column14, COLUMN15 = @column15 where CREATED_TIMESTAMP = @createdTimestamp
